&lt;p data-start=&quot;148&quot; data-end=&quot;160&quot;&gt;InMobi Exchange (IX) is one of the world&#39;s largest mobile ad exchanges, serving tens of thousands of apps and delivering more than 100 billion impressions every month. Now, we&#39;re making a decisive move into one of the fastest-growing and most transformative sectors in digital advertising — commerce and retail media. We are building a scaled Commerce Exchange from the ground up, and we&#39;re looking for a senior product leader who can define this vision end-to-end and turn it into a market-shaping business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]&quot;&gt;As Director, Product Management – Commerce Exchange, you will own the strategy and full execution for IX&#39;s commerce products across retailers, merchants, and retail media networks. Your remit spans buy-side capabilities, commerce and audience data integrations, attribution and measurement solutions, and the acquisition and activation of high-intent omnichannel supply. You will define how IX becomes the most performant, transparent, and measurable environment for commerce advertisers across the full funnel.&lt;/p&gt;
