&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Overview of the Role:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Accelerate is InMobi&#39;s AI-native omnichannel advertising platform built for SMBs and agencies. Designed from the ground up to be truly self-serve, Accelerate uses AI to create, manage, and optimize campaigns across channels — learning from every client interaction to deliver a platform experience that makes sophisticated advertising accessible without deep expertise or manual intervention.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As Director of Product Management, U.S. Market, you will be the product intelligence and self-serve authority that shapes how Accelerate is experienced by advertisers — from SMBs managing their own growth to agencies running campaigns on behalf of clients. You understand both audiences deeply: how they evaluate and adopt self-serve advertising platforms, what drives their success, and what stands in their way. You translate that understanding through an AI-first product lens into decisions that meaningfully drive adoption and retention.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work in close partnership with our GTM, PMM, and Engineering teams. You bring the market depth; the platform team delivers the build. Reporting directly to the Head of Product, Accelerate, and based on-site in our San Mateo, CA office, this is a high-visibility, high-impact role at the intersection of market strategy and product execution.&lt;/p&gt;
